763-2}}\n* [[Andrea Tornielli]]. ''Pio XII. Eugenio Pacelli. Un uomo sul trono di Pietro''. Mondadori 2007, pp.&nbsp;661,\n* Andrea Tornielli e [[Matteo Luigi Napolitano]]. ''Pacelli, Roncalli e i battesimi della Shoah'', Piemme, Casale Monferrato 2005, {{ISBN|88-384-1043-7}}\n\n== U ==\n{{Empty section|date=July 2010}}\n\n== V ==\n* [[Guido Verucci]]. ''La chiesa nella societ\u00e0 contemporanea''. Laterza, Bari-Roma 1999. {{ISBN|88-420-3007-4}}\n\n== W ==\n* [[Garry Wills]] ''Papal Sin. Structures of Deceit [Peccato pontificio. Strutture d\u2019inganno]'', Doubleday, New York 2000.\n\n== X ==\n{{Empty section|date=July 2010}}\n\n== Y ==\n{{Empty section|date=July 2010}}\n\n== Z ==\n* [[Susan Zuccotti]], ''Proprio sotto le sue finestre. Il Vaticano e l\u2019olocausto in Italia'', Mondadori, Milano 2002. {{ISBN|88-424-9810-6}}\n\n== See also ==\n* [[Bibliography of World War II]]\n{{Pope Pius XII}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Pius XII}}\n[[Category:Books about Pope Pius XII|*]]\n[[Category:Christian bibliographies|Pius 12]]\n[[Category:Bibliographies of people]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikipedia bibliography}}\n{{main|Pope Pius XII}}\nThis '''bibliography on Church policies 1939&ndash;1945'''{{clarify|date=May 2019}} includes mainly [[Italy|Italian]] publications relative to [[Pope Pius XII]] and [[Holy See|Vatican]] policies during [[World War II]] . Two areas are missing and need separate bibliographies at a later date.\n\n* The bibliography does not include theology, theological issues and publications on the [[Theology of Pope Pius XII]], [[Mariology of Pope Pius XII]], on his ecclesiastical promulgations such as the [[Dogma (Roman Catholic)|dogma]] of the [[Assumption of Mary|Assumption]] of the [[Blessed Virgin Mary (Roman Catholic)|Virgin Mary]], [[Pope Pius XII Liturgy Reforms|Church reforms]], or, the [[Beatifications of Pope Pius XII]] [[Saints canonized by Pope Pius XII]], [[List of encyclicals of Pope Pius XII|Encyclicals of the Pontiff]] and other the